, we waited to see what would happen.<br><br>XA botched it, and were wiped out...their last remaining clerics were outside of VS's room, and he was running around killing them.  ToV crammed into the back of the prep room, for fear of being trained.  Sure enough, the last remaining member of XA's raid party, Skyjulin, with VS aggro on her, ran directly into our midst and died.  VS proceeded to wipe us out.<br><br>10 minutes later we were rezzed up, with another 10 people coming in, and we went in and took down VS on our own, while XA rezed their raid party.  XA claimed Skyjulin was trying to get out to camp.  The GMs could do nothing, since they werent there to witness it.<br><br>Friday, we heard that Trakanon had popped, but Vision was already going in after her, with XA's help, so we ignored it more or less.  Once we heard that Vision had failed though, we decided to go check things out.  We showed up (about 8 of us) at Sebilis, and an officer in Vision told us that we could have an uninturrupted attempt at Trak if we helped them with CR.  We agreed, grabbed a mage and headed in.  Along for the ride was an Exiled Alliance cleric (whose name escapes me atm).  We never questioned him, assuming he was there to rez people dead in the lair once we took down Trak.<br><br>A total of 40 of us were assembled at the final prep spot before Trak's lair, going over last minute tactics.  The XA cleric had set up camp across the river, within sight of Trak.  As we moved up to the last corner before the lair, Trak came charging around the corner at us.  Needless to say, we all died due to bad positioning (though we still got him to gate on us).<br><br>The only conclusion we could come to was that XA had yet again trained us, since we'd never had Trak aggro on us like that before, and had already set him up for the rush.  The cleric must have cast an aggresive spell on trak from where he sat, wiping us out.  Vision and XA then moved in and killed Trak, while we summoned corpses and rezzed before heading out.<br><br>Twice in 24 hours, what appears to be intentional training of raid parties to gain advantage by Exiled Alliance.  Take it for what you will. <p><HR WIDTH="50%" ALIGN="LEFT"><IMG SRC="http://outside.clanpages.com/podside.jpg" ALIGN="left" HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=100><br><b>Ullric Littleblade</b><br>Assassin of Tides of Valor<br><A HREF="http://www.thesafehouse.org">Ayonae Ro Ring Warden</A><BR>Master of the Jade Hand<BR><i><A HREF="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=83046">"Speed kills if y'know what I mean."</A></i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/usphirekblackstaff.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sphirek Blackstaff</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Boardfellow</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/26/01 7:23:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=626.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re:</span><hr size=1> You failed trak with 40 people?<br>wow <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uetirnaltwigz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Etirnal Twigz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/26/01 7:27:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=626.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re:</span><hr size=1> Sphirek know how to read?? <p><center><img src="http://members.home.net/ggothlin/Base22.bmp"><center><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=5241">Click Here To View My Equip</a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=